title: Number of Burger King restaurants in the Asia Pacific region from 2012 to 2013
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 12 different Countrys on X-axis for 2 groups 2012, and 2013. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Country Australia had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 2 groups, and it was for 2013. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Country Philippines for 2012.
In Country Australia, 2012 had the maximum SOME LABEL and it saw the lowest in Country Philippines out of all 12 Countrys.
The maximum SOME LABEL for 2012 that was found in Country Australia was 12.31 times larger than the minimum SOME LABEL observed in Country Philippines.
